Invocation Name: wedding day
des:
On October 15, 1978 Rusty and Sharon said I do and became husband and wife. Now, in memory of them, their son Jason will say I do to his soul mate exactly 42 years after his parents did. 

We have been talking about and planning this day forever now it seems. I can't wait to be his wife!!
